These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, fanta, milk
Sport: water-polo, cricket, climbing, sailing
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Sport:climbing##1
2. Sport:sailing is on the far left##1
3. Sport:climbing is between Sport:cricket and Beverage:soy-milk##2
4. Beverage:milk is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:fanta is between Beverage:soy-milk and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk         | soy-milk   | fanta | hot-chocolate       |
| Sport      | sailing | water-polo | climbing   | cricket |

