.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: rock-climbing, writing, skydiving, card-games
Nationality: argentine, italian, chinese, french
1. Nationality:french is between Hobby:skydiving and Nationality:italian##2
2. Hobby:card-games is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:chinese is on the right of Nationality:argentine##1
4. Hobby:rock-climbing is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | writing | rock-climbing | skydiving | card-games |
| Nationality   | italian    | french   | argentine | chinese       |

