3. Nationality:indian is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:italian is on the left of Food:pineapple##1
5. Food:zucchini == Nationality:italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | spinach | zucchini   | pineapple  |
| Nationality   | indian | polish   | italian | argentine |

